00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:33.160
It's as long as it flows in a single direction, and there's no cycles or circles, then you

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:36.640
can connect as many data frames as you'd like.

00:05:36.640 --> 00:05:41.160
