00:05:52.959 --> 00:05:57.239
And then I had a third output just to prove that they're disconnected, but there is a

00:05:57.239 --> 00:05:59.399
chain of command that can happen.

00:05:59.399 --> 00:06:04.359
So add as many as you want, just as long as there isn't a cycle.

